OL,6,FEverleigh had been left alone in her
OL,7,Ffather's care on the night of 20 April
OL,8,F2021 and was "only just" breathing
OL,9,Fwhen her grandmother, Kelly Stroud,
OL,10,Fcalled an ambulance the next morning.
OL,12,FHolford was "under the influence" of
OL,13,Fcannabis at the time of the shaking,
OL,14,Fand later lied to police about his
OL,15,Fdrug use having smoked at least five
OL,16,Fjoints to celebrate "420" the previous
OL,17,Fday, which the court had heard he
OL,18,Fagreed was a "big day for cannabis
OL,19,Fsmokers".
