OL,6,FWhile his baby was rushed to Queen
OL,7,FElizabeth the Queen Mother Hospital in
OL,8,FMargate, Kent, on 21 April, he showed
OL,9,F"little emotion" and continued to
OL,10,Fdownload and play games on his phone,
OL,11,Fjurors heard.
OL,13,FOn Thursday, Holford, of Ramsgate, was
OL,14,Ffound unanimously guilty of murder and
OL,15,Factual bodily harm of his daughter by
OL,16,Fa Canterbury Crown Court jury.
