OL,4,Cby shaking her jailed for life
OL,6,FOn Friday (4 July), Mr Justice Michael
OL,7,FFordham sentenced Holford to life
OL,8,Fimprisonment with a minimum term of 16
OL,9,Fyears and told the court that he had
OL,10,F"robbed" his former partner and her
OL,11,Ffamily of "any type of deep happiness"
OL,12,Ffor the rest of their lives.
OL,14,FThe judge said: "Overnight on 20th to
OL,15,F21st of April 2021 when you were just
OL,16,F20 years old you shook your five-week-
OL,17,Fold baby daughter Everleigh.
