OL,6,FEverleigh, who was born on 13 March
OL,7,F2021, spent more than a year in
OL,8,Fhospital before she died aged 14
OL,9,Fmonths on 27 May 2022.
OL,11,FMr Justice Fordham continued: "Kelly
OL,12,FStroud has described in her statement
OL,13,Fthe impacts of what you did, how your
OL,14,Factions denied Everleigh a life, how
OL,15,Fyour actions denied a lifetime of
OL,16,Fhopes and dreams to Casey, a wonderful
OL,17,Fyoung mum who never gave up fighting
OL,18,Ffor her daughter."
