OL,6,F"The shock was something that they
OL,7,Fhave not experienced before, albeit
OL,8,Fthey had a short period of denial and
OL,9,Fdesperately searched for answers,"
OL,10,Fsaid prosecutor Eloise Marshall KC.
OL,12,FThe statement read: "In a blink of an
OL,13,Feye our world came crashing down in
OL,14,Fthe most heartbreaking and traumatic
OL,15,Fway."
OL,17,FHolford also received a two-year
OL,18,Fconcurrent prison sentence for actual
OL,19,Fbodily harm of Everleigh's anus which
